{"TopicId":178604,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Space Center View Controls","CreatedByName":"Ismakefire","CreatedById":192148,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-28T15:38:58Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Ismakefire","CreatedById":192148,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-28T15:38:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow can I rotate my view in the Kerbal Space Center Screen?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI recently returned from flight and did something with the mouse and keyboard to rotate the camera in a way to make several of the buildings block each other.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWASD and arrow keys seem to strafe, while mouse wheel zooms, but I can\u0027t seem to figure out how to rotate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks so much for your help! Searching variants of \u0022Ksp Space Center Controls\u0022 has only been yielding different in-game controls.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-28T15:48:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHold the right mouse button down while you move the mouse.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, and welcome to the forums!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-09-28T15:49:01Z\u0022 title=\u002209/28/2018 03:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 28, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Geonovast\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ismakefire","CreatedById":192148,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-28T16:13:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223459179\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178604\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221538149719\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 minutes ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHold the right mouse button down while you move the mouse.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, and welcome to the forums!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh! I\u0027m using a track pad, so I don\u0027t think I can even do that \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EThanks Geonovast!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-28T16:18:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223459197\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178604\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221538151223\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192148\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ismakefire\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Ismakefire said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh! I\u0027m using a track pad, so I don\u0027t think I can even do that \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EThanks Geonovast!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYour track pad should have a designated area for a right click, even if you don\u0027t have a separate button.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo yourself a favor and go get a mouse!\u00A0 They\u0027re like $4 new and I see them at thrift stores all the time for like $0.50.\u00A0 Even a crappy mouse will be worlds different than a trackpad.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-28T16:55:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait.... how do you zoom??\u00A0\u00A0 How are you even playing the game without a mousewheel???\u00A0 The \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E would be a huge pain, almost unplayable.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223459197\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178604\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221538151223\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192148\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ismakefire\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n41 minutes ago, Ismakefire said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nO\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Eh! I\u0027m using a trac\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Ek pad, s\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Eo I don\u0027t think I can even \u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Edo t\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Ehat\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E!\u003C/span\u0